It was always full of Rottnmeier for me, you know?

295
00:21:11,412 --> 00:21:14,412
It's so boring that I don't know how to stand it.

296
00:21:14,412 --> 00:21:16,412
Always full of Rottnmeier.

297
00:21:16,412 --> 00:21:19,412
I can't stand her eternal warmth anymore.

