I thought about everything again.

301
00:21:33,438 --> 00:21:34,438
I'll stay here.

302
00:21:34,438 --> 00:21:35,438
Yes?

303
00:21:35,438 --> 00:21:37,438
Yes, for at least a few more days.

304
00:21:40,438 --> 00:21:42,438
For sure?

305
00:21:42,438 --> 00:21:43,438
I'll stay here.

