suitcase full.

308
00:21:55,158 --> 00:21:58,158
Heidi, I'm so happy.

309
00:21:59,158 --> 00:22:04,158
Can you help me, Clara, that I get all the things when I want to go home?

310
00:22:04,158 --> 00:22:07,158
Yes, of course, I'll do that.

311
00:22:07,158 --> 00:22:09,158
Mrs. Clara!

312
00:22:09,158 --> 00:22:11,158
Heidemarie!

313
00:22:11,158 --> 00:22:13,158
Uh, Adelheid.

314
00:22:13,158 --> 00:22:16,158
Heidemarie is not bad either.

315
00:22:16,158 --> 00:22:18,158
I like Heidi better.

316
00:22:18,158 --> 00:22:20,158
Do you know how we can call her?

317
00:22:20,158 --> 00:22:21,158
No, how?

318
00:22:21,158 --> 00:22:23,158
We just call her Mrs. Warmth.

319
00:22:25,158 --> 00:22:26,166
Yes, we do.

320
00:22:26,166 --> 00:22:31,166
He's been awake for half an hour. Oh, warm-up, my nerves can't stand it.

321
00:22:31,166 --> 00:22:37,166
And this terrible child has messed it all up. And this noise. Discipline!

322
00:22:41,166 --> 00:22:45,166
So Heidi had decided to stay in the Sesemann house.

323
00:22:45,166 --> 00:22:48,166
She got along well with Clara, even with the schoolteacher,

324
00:22:48,166 --> 00:22:51,166
if she only knew what he wanted from her.

325
00:22:51,166 --> 00:22:55,084
At home in the mountains, she had never asked anyone about all the strange
things.

326
00:22:55,084 --> 00:22:58,764
Heidi found the life here in this house sometimes very strange.

327
00:22:58,764 --> 00:23:00,164
Everything was so difficult.

328
00:23:00,164 --> 00:23:02,524
They made the simplest things wrong.

329
00:23:02,524 --> 00:23:06,124
They locked birds in cages and were angry when they were released.

330
00:23:06,124 --> 00:23:09,204
And even a rottmeyer, who always knew everything,

331
00:23:09,204 --> 00:23:12,484
didn't want to see that birds fly better outside than inside.

332
00:23:12,484 --> 00:23:14,644
And then there was the thing with the mice.

333
00:23:14,644 --> 00:23:16,284
After all, mice are hungry too.

334
00:23:16,284 --> 00:23:19,644
But we want to tell you about that in our next story.

